shing blow. If the foe turns out to be too strong, Octillery spews ink to escape."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"The ink it spits when escaping is special. It contains a substance that dulls the sense of smell, so Pok\u00e9mon with keen noses get lost."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It usually sleeps in caves. The pitch-black ink that Octillery spits is also used for cooking."},{"version":"sword","text":"It has a tendency to want to be in holes. It prefers rock crags or pots and sprays ink from them before attacking."},{"version":"shield","text":"It traps enemies with its suction-cupped tentacles, then smashes them with its rock-hard head."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"While Octillery still shoots water from its mouth, the drastic anatomical difference between it and Remoraid meant that for a long time, no one believed the former evolved from the latter."}],"evo":{"name":"remoraid","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"octillery","level":1,"min_level":25,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/224.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/224.png","capture":75,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"attack":1,"special_attack":1},"forms":[]}